data.description: Large 5BR/3BA split foyer Ranch located on a sprawling lot in Hillcrest Orchards. Pull into the double wide driveway, make your way to the entry into your forever home.  Open the door into an entry that leads up to the main floor or down to the additional living space.  The main floor beams with tons of natural light and hardwood flooring.  The large living room is open to the spacious dining room that leads to the kitchen. The kitchen boasts plenty of cabinets, sleek white countertops, stainless steel appliances, and a deep sink under a window.  Down the hall are two sizable secondary bedrooms, a full bath, and a large primary suite featuring a private full bath. The lower level is finished offering two additional bedrooms with above grade windows, a full bath, a large family room, laundry, storage, and access to the spacious yard.  From the main floor open the sliding doors onto an oversized tiered deck that overlooks a fenced yard filled with tons of green space, and two sheds. This home has so much to offer new homeowners including updated electric, new property fencing, recently remodeled basement including bathroom, and new washing machine.  Imagine all this and in close proximity to shopping, restaurants, and commuter routes.
